      &lt;img alt="YouTube’s logo with geometric design in the background" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-NUhvB2E77B-asDHXP_PzX3_DJk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73719153/acastro_STK092_04.0.jpg" /&gt;
